Marsh & McLennan Cos., the second-
largest insurance broker, named Bill Pieroni as chief operating
officer of its flagship unit, reporting to Peter Zaffino.  Pieroni joins from State Farm Mutual Automobile Insurance
Co., where he was a senior vice president, the New York-based
brokerage said today in a statement distributed by  Business
Wire .  To contact the reporter on this story:
